{"tid":2198630,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［廣東話］好唔好食唔食應唔應該洗唔洗","createTime":"2020-09-11T13:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T04:18:17.000Z","uid":58612,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"314dadeede41bb07f3007590aed5dbfb38dae659","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:11:44.000Z","msg":"好唔好、玩唔玩、應唔應該既正同負面回答都用返問句入面個字，ie 好/唔好；食/唔食；應該/唔應該，點解淨係得「洗唔洗」既正面回答唔會講「洗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喂你洗唔洗人幫呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <strong><span class=\"red\">要呀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好苦惱，到底點解唔會答「洗呀」咁樣！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244a4677ba65d11a5bd4cf825d286f0b7f1d70e8","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752c4f09dd2272024191fac97350c7d6dce69af0","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:17:18.000Z","msg":"有冇語言學jj可以說明下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19c0e3f9f6c9925f1a73cbff9e650cf6aae77ca","tid":2198630,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"你都講咗個答案出嚟啦<br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗 係本質上唔係疑問句<br />\n<br />\n你舉嘅 好唔好、玩唔玩、應唔應該 係可以單獨成為疑問<br />\n<br />\n而洗唔洗之後要再加嘢 e.g. 洗唔洗人幫<br />\n<br />\n如果就咁「洗唔洗呀?」就唔係疑問意思"},{"pid":"e5415d273e5b4767c7ba7d86605d48d15e6080eb","tid":2198630,"uid":42374,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"未聽過人咁問會答要呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8036323ae357df7aec8cdbee62f0bdb047b3175","tid":2198630,"uid":128102,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"不嬲都答洗<br />\n樓主邊到鄉下？"},{"pid":"13a9a9f58e6bdc735733cc74c39b8ad5e4f633f3","tid":2198630,"uid":69844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"愛唔愛"},{"pid":"22682bb7dd6427d85f7865b5bbfe370d4785c8bb","tid":2198630,"uid":285515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔會答洗？<br />\n我俾人咁問都會答洗"},{"pid":"3b79ad06b48f405f9c37ab785aa61188de7c33d5","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22682bb7dd6427d85f7865b5bbfe370d4785c8bb","tid":2198630,"uid":285515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔會答洗？<br />\n我俾人咁問都會答洗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"如果有人問你「洗唔洗幫你call白車」<br />\n你肯定你既即時反應唔係「call啦仆街」而係「洗呀仆街」????"},{"pid":"54e7544021ef9394309700625ab47768ece1ed26","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c19c0e3f9f6c9925f1a73cbff9e650cf6aae77ca","tid":2198630,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"你都講咗個答案出嚟啦<br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗 係本質上唔係疑問句<br />\n<br />\n你舉嘅 好唔好、玩唔玩、應唔應該 係可以單獨成為疑問<br />\n<br />\n而洗唔洗之後要再加嘢 e.g. 洗唔洗人幫<br />\n<br />\n如果就咁「洗唔洗呀?」就唔係疑問意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"假設問果個真係唔知答案, 「洗唔洗」同「好唔好」都係疑問句黎嫁喎<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，如果「洗唔洗呀」係果D感嘆句, 回答者都唔會講「洗呀」嫁，試下呢個例子：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：搞到個party咁串，洗唔洗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會答「就係要搞到咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」定係「就係洗搞到咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」？"},{"pid":"d0c4049808a1fe64cc58ce5a0abea01b1f766852","tid":2198630,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3b79ad06b48f405f9c37ab785aa61188de7c33d5","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22682bb7dd6427d85f7865b5bbfe370d4785c8bb","tid":2198630,"uid":285515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔會答洗？<br />\n我俾人咁問都會答洗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"如果有人問你「洗唔洗幫你call白車」<br />\n你肯定你既即時反應唔係「call啦仆街」而係「洗呀仆街」????"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"你咩省份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未聽過香港人咁講嘢"},{"pid":"bf5744762a344049fef432e1d3437b917f200ae6","tid":2198630,"uid":60808,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"你啲碗洗唔洗啊？<br />\n洗！"},{"pid":"f3029e0e47e707d853fcb07e81a3de77956a8c4a","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:09:26.000Z","msg":"場景一：傷心毒撚：如果我冇溝MK仔條女，我洗比人打柒？<br />\n場景二：傷心毒撚：如果我冇溝MK仔條女，我會比人打柒？<br />\n<br />\n想像下身旁安慰佢既清醒毒撚：<span class=\"red\">會</span>呀，因為你柒過龍，個個見到都想打鳩你。<br />\n兩個場景下，清醒毒撚會講「洗呀」嫁咩？唔係「會呀」更合符語感咩？"},{"pid":"6241ae6d96a1543377b31608085a0701895c06aa","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5744762a344049fef432e1d3437b917f200ae6","tid":2198630,"uid":60808,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"你啲碗洗唔洗啊？<br />\n洗！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"呢個洗字係當「清潔」解，唔同case啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002e5b71340062df140d5d26cdc112fcda494b51","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79076f6d9f3a896c749a5ce8e6f4666228dcae4f","tid":2198630,"uid":58612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"輕pish"},{"pid":"a0e47e6f7482203151cfa92a8d5bc6bdb0571d46","tid":2198630,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T01:04:08.000Z","msg":"唔係通常答「好呀唔該」嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔使咪答「唔使」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35f551a80d947092a163e5e53e63c9d57138cd8","tid":2198630,"uid":14566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T01:04:44.000Z","msg":"Yes = 要<br />\nNo = 唔洗"},{"pid":"a13fd093095abc2c0998a5827ab1f9c3e2b14118","tid":2198630,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T03:49:20.000Z","msg":"你洗唔洗衫呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n洗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2731d89321ea0bb6493e1fedf20a8d3d8ca54330","tid":2198630,"uid":134247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:02:29.000Z","msg":"其他粵語嘅方言可能仲保留咗<br />\n使唔使 - 使呀 呢個講法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2acfa3ce48352c2ec8782351f509541207803e7","tid":2198630,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"講開要唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要唔要人幫"},{"pid":"c3940d39d7e932100dbf928e33971c39ffe95312","tid":2198630,"uid":275161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:06:03.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗=要唔要<br />\n<br />\n要 唔會講做洗<br />\n但唔要 會講做唔洗"},{"pid":"e9d1f800aac01cf993f29bfd3d7421e5250fb3f9","tid":2198630,"uid":257576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"我多數答「好呀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4ef86ace215d9339fdde6abea30baebad4c8fe","tid":2198630,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗錢？<br />\n洗呀"},{"pid":"bc42155270ede88ce4070c32e9d152b171b30724","tid":2198630,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"英文答一個「Yes」就夠，我諗廣東話會用「係呀」、「好呀（Yes）」或者「要呀」。<br />\n<br />\n樓句嘅例句牽涉「係」以外嘅動詞所以唔會用「係呀」；「好呀」都係常見答法，不贅；「要呀」應該係因為廣泛使用，從一個specific（需要）嘅用法，弱化為簡單嘅肯定「Yes」。<br />\n<br />\n至於答「使呀」，都可以表達到你要人幫，但因為少人用，所以有highlight嘅作用。我想像到嘅情況係，你嘅情況危急到唔使問都知要幫，答「使呀」有諷刺或者強調嘅作用。<br />\n<br />\n進一步嚟講，如果句子係「使唔使幫你叫白車」。由邊個嚟叫白車唔係重點，總之係是旦一個就得，所以唔會答「幫呀」，除非你一定要某個人幫你嗌；「使呀」用法上一段講咗（唔排除有其他情況會用到）；「好呀」「要呀」「叫啦」都係可能嘅答法。<br />\n<br />\n至於點解「叫」要用「啦」唔用「呀」，我推測可能因為Yes或No先會用「呀」，如果動詞都用「呀」，代表你真係好嬲（「食呀」「走呀」），正常祈使句嘅動詞都係用「啦」就夠。"}]}